                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
                    What about maintenance?
                </h2>
                <div
                    class="bg-gray-900 border border-sky-500/30 p-8 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-sky-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-lg"
